parts: Research into the tuition centers in Singapore that have an emphasis on Junior College or Upper Secondary Mathematics tuition. Shortlist those which potentially are looking for new hires and create a table with their contact details including how to submit applications and resumes.

Could you specify whether you're looking for tuition centers that focus on:

- Junior College (JC) Mathematics only, Upper Secondary (O-Level/IP) Mathematics only, or both?
- Specialization in certain types of Mathematics (e.g., H2 Math, Additional Math, Further Math)?
- Specific locations within Singapore (or islandwide)?

Also, do you prefer large established centers or are you open to smaller or newer tuition centers? This will help refine the search.

Lastly, do you have any preference for part-time, full-time, or contract positions?

metadata.async_task_prompt:
Find tuition centers in Singapore that focus on Junior College (JC) and Upper Secondary (O-Level/IP) Mathematics tuition, including H1 and H2 Mathematics, Additional Math, and Elementary Mathematics. 

Identify centers that are currently or potentially hiring for full-time, part-time, or contract teaching positions. 

Provide a table including:
- Name of tuition center
- Website
- Location(s)
- Contact details (phone, email, or any relevant links)
- How to apply (e.g., email, online application form, LinkedIn, etc.)

Include both large established centers and smaller, growing centers across Singapore. Prioritize centers with active job postings but also include those that indicate they are open to hiring tutors.

parts:
# Tuition Centres for JC & Upper Secondary Math in Singapore Below is a list of tuition centres in Singapore that focus on Junior College (H1/H2) and Upper Secondary (O-Level/IP) Mathematics (including Additional & Elementary Math). Each entry includes their website, location(s), contact info, and how to apply for teaching positions (full-time, part-time, or contract). Both large established centres and smaller specialist centres are included. Centres with active job postings or indications of hiring are prioritized, but those open to hiring tutors are also listed. | **Name of Centre** | **Website** | **Location(s)** | **Contact Details** | **How to Apply** | |------------------------------|-----------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------| | **Mind Stretcher** – (multi-subject, includes Sec/JC Math) | | *26 branches islandwide* (Central, North, North-East, East, West)【49†L24-L32】 | Email: enquiries@mindstretcher.com【56†L53-L59】
(Branch-specific hotlines available) | Email your resume to **hr@mindstretcher.com**【54†L100-L104】 (or visit the careers page on their website for open positions). | | **Zenith Education Studio** – (JC & Secondary specialist) | | *8 centres islandwide* (e.g. Bishan, Bukit Timah, Buona Vista, Marymount, Paya Lebar, Tampines)【58†L128-L136】 | Tel: +65 8768 7651
Email: hello@LearnAtZenith.com【58†L110-L118】 | Apply via the **Zenith Careers** page (online application – *“See Open Roles”*)【59†L33-L41】 on their website. | | **Learners’ Lodge** – (IP & JC tuition specialist) | | Ang Mo Kio, *Bishan*, *Jurong*, *Kembangan*, *Kovan* (Hougang), *Marymount*【46†L374-L382】【46†L384-L392】 | Tel: +65 9119 9655
Email: enquiries@qeducation.sg【46†L366-L374】 | Email your full resume to **admin@learnerslodge.com.sg**【33†L91-L94】 (as indicated on their “Join Us” page) to apply. | | **Raymond’s Math & Science Studio (RMSS)** – (Sec & JC Math/Science) | | *5 branches:* Bishan, Marine Parade (Parkway Centre), Punggol, Jurong, Kovan【20†L73-L81】 | Tel: +65 6222 8222
Email: contactus@rmss.com.sg【19†L3-L7】 | Submit an application via the **RMSS Careers** page (online form)【10†L27-L35】【10†L54-L62】 on their website. | | **The Maths Lab** – (Math specialist for Sec; some JC topics) | | *4 branches:* Bukit Timah, Tiong Bahru, Kovan, Bedok【3†L8-L16】 | Tel: +65 6475 0624【68†L49-L57】 | WhatsApp **9660 7113** or email **TheMathLabHR@gmail.com**【4†L19-L27】 (HR contact) to apply for teaching positions. | | **Achevas** – (A-Level/JC H2 & IP/O-Level Math specialist) | | *3 centres:* Jurong East, Hougang, Marine Parade【69†L33-L40】 | Tel: +65 8648 6582
Email: learn@achevas.com【69†L13-L18】 | Email your CV to **hr@achevas.com**【23†L84-L90】 to apply for available Math tutor/teacher positions. | | **Future Academy** – (Secondary & JC tuition, ex-MOE tutors) | | *3 centres:* Bugis (Bencoolen), Bukit Timah (Beauty World), Toa Payoh【43†L290-L298】【43†L300-L304】 | Tel: +65 6884 6566 / +65 8457 7888
Email: info@fa.edu.sg【43†L284-L292】 | Contact the centre via email with your resume (they hire highly qualified tutors) – **info@fa.edu.sg**【43†L284-L292】. | | **AO Studies** – (Math & Physics specialist for O & A Levels) | | *1 centre:* Bugis (420 North Bridge Road)【63†L27-L31】 | Tel: +65 9022 6662
Email: joseph.ang@aostudies.com.sg【63†L27-L32】 | Email the centre (Attn: Joseph Ang) with your resume to inquire about tutor positions【63†L27-L32】. (*Note:* AO Studies maintains in-house specialist tutors and does not use freelance tutors【66†L1-L4】.) | Each of these centres offers tuition for Upper Sec and/or JC Math (e.g. H2 Math, H1 Math, Additional and E. Math) and has indicated either active hiring or openness to hiring tutors. Be sure to check their official careers pages or contact them directly for the latest job openings and application procedures. Sources for the information above are provided in the citations.
